standard_anchor(im_kindergarten_u7_l5, im_lesson, "IM-GK-U7-L5",
    "IM Kindergarten Unit 7 Lesson 5: Story Problems about Shapes. The purpose of this lesson is for students to solve Add To, Result Unknown and Take From, Result Unknown story problems about pattern blocks. Goals: Choose strategies for solving Add To, Result Unknown and Take From, Result Unknown problems and represent the problem with an equation. | Match (orally) story problems and equations.").
standard_anchor(im_kindergarten_u7_l6, im_lesson, "IM-GK-U7-L6",
