standard_anchor(im_kindergarten_u7_l16, im_lesson, "IM-GK-U7-L16",
    "IM Kindergarten Unit 7 Lesson 16: Represent the Classroom with Shapes. The purpose of this lesson is for students to use solid shapes to make a model of the classroom. Goals: Create and describe (orally) models of the classroom, using solid shapes.").
