standard_anchor(im_grade5_u3_l1, im_lesson, "IM-G5-U3-L1",
    "IM Grade5 Unit 3 Lesson 1: One Piece of One Part. The purpose of this lesson is for students to interpret and represent a unit fraction of a unit fraction with diagrams. Goals: Represent a unit fraction of a unit fraction of a whole with a diagram and interpret (orally and in writing) the diagram.").
standard_anchor(im_grade5_u3_l2, im_lesson, "IM-G5-U3-L2",
    "IM Grade5 Unit 3 Lesson 2: Represent Unit Fraction Multiplication. The purpose of this lesson is for students to write and evaluate expressions given a diagram that represents the product of two unit fractions. Goals: Compare and contrast (orally and in writing) diagrams that represent           and          . | Describe (orally and in writing) how diagrams and expressions represent the product of 2 unit fractions.").
standard_anchor(im_grade5_u3_l3, im_lesson, "IM-G5-U3-L3",
    "IM Grade5 Unit 3 Lesson 3: Multiply Unit Fractions. The purpose of this lesson is for students to represent products of unit fractions using diagrams and equations. Goals: Calculate the product of 2 unit fractions. | Interpret (orally and in writing) a diagram and an equation that represent the product of 2 unit fractions.").
standard_anchor(im_grade5_u3_l4, im_lesson, "IM-G5-U3-L4",
