standard_anchor(im_grade5_u3_l13, im_lesson, "IM-G5-U3-L13",
    "IM Grade5 Unit 3 Lesson 13: Divide Whole Numbers by Unit Fractions. The purpose of this lesson is for students to solve division problems in a way that makes sense to them. Goals: Compare and contrast (using words and other representations) strategies for finding the quotient of a whole number and a unit fraction in context. | Represent a situation with an equation involving the division of a whole number by a unit fraction and interpret (orally and in wri").
standard_anchor(im_grade5_u3_l14, im_lesson, "IM-G5-U3-L14",
    "IM Grade5 Unit 3 Lesson 14: Represent Division of Whole Numbers by Unit Fractions. The purpose of this lesson is for students to solve problems involving division of a whole number by a unit fraction and write equations to represent them. Goals: Compare and contrast (orally and in writing) diagrams and equations that represent dividing a whole number by a fraction. | Generalize (orally and in writing) that .").
standard_anchor(im_grade5_u3_l15, im_lesson, "IM-G5-U3-L15",
    "IM Grade5 Unit 3 Lesson 15: Fraction Division Situations. The purpose of this lesson is for students to write and solve problems that involve dividing a whole number by a unit fraction and a unit fraction by a whole number. Goals: Generate (in writing) a situation to represent a division expression with a whole number and a unit fraction. | Match (orally and in writing) situations and expressions that represent a whole number divided by a unit fraction.").
standard_anchor(im_grade5_u3_l16, im_lesson, "IM-G5-U3-L16",
    "IM Grade5 Unit 3 Lesson 16: Reason about Quotients. The purpose of this lesson is for students to find quotients involving a whole number and a unit fraction and assess the reasonableness of their answers. Goals: Critique (orally) explanations of strategies used to determine the size of a quotient when dividing a whole number by a unit fraction. | Explain (orally and in writing) strategies for determining whether a quotient involving a whole number and a unit fraction is greater or less t").
standard_anchor(im_grade5_u3_l17, im_lesson, "IM-G5-U3-L17",
